Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This Heritage property is located on the corner of Water Street and Holloway Street directly across from Raymond’s Restaurant. It features two floors of executive office space with a reception area, office, boardroom and kitchen on the main floor and additional offices and open work space on the second floor. There are two private parking spots at the rear of the building.In addition to office space, the building also has an executive style apartment on the third floor that is fully furnished with high end fixtures.
